@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hudbwe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp((0.57 - (v1 + 0.48 * tmp + 0.59)))
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.31 - v0 + 0.89)) + 0.56)
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.57 + tmp + 0.37)) * 0.09)
    v1 = wp.sin((tmp * wp.exp(v1 + 0.71)))
    v0 = v0
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.02) - wp.exp(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
